[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "改めて、ありがとね。\n色々、私たち家族のために動いてくれて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "いいえ。当たり前のことをしたまでです",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……変な家族だったでしょ。\nあんたの家って、どんな感じだったの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "私の家は、温かい家庭でした。ですが、両親は\n私が幼い頃に魔物に襲われて星になってしまいました",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……悪いこと聞いちゃったな。ごめん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "お気になさらないでください。\n両親に注がれた愛は、今も私の中に生きていますから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そっか。強いね、カロリンは",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "それに、孤児として預けられた教会は\n第２の我が家のようなものです。寂しくはありません",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "教会が家か。カロリンらしいね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "銃を手に取り戦うと決めたのも、\nその家庭を守りたいという思いからでした",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……そっちは、ちょっとやりすぎな気もするけど",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ハイディも、私にとってはその家庭の一部です",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "あはは……なんか、教会から逃げ出したのが\n申し訳なくなってきた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "気にしなくて大丈夫です。\n誰しも迷う時はありますから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "せめて、一言くらいは挨拶しておこうかな。\n教会、久しぶりに行ってみるか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……！　ワンワン！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "お、ヴァレリア……！　まだ元気そうだな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "もう老犬ですが食欲は旺盛です。\nさすがヴァレリアですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ほんとだ、さすがだよ。まさか同じ名前の相棒まで、\n食いしん坊になるとは思ってなかったけど",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おや……誰かいらっしゃったのですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "マザーシスター、お久しぶりです。\nハイディが帰ってきました",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "マザーシスター",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それはそれは。なんと喜ばしいことでしょう。\n元気そうで何より",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……逃げた私を、責めたりしないんだね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "マザーシスターは、\nいつも皆を温かく迎えてくださいます",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "それに、ここ以外に逃げられる場所があるのなら、\nきっとそこに居たほうが幸せでしょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ここは、すべてから見放された方を\n受けとめる場所なのですから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "マザーシスター",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "だとしても、いつでも帰ってきていいのですからね。\nここはもう、あなたの家なのですから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ここで過ごした日々のことは、今でも覚えてる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "お嬢様だった私に、生き方を教えてくれた。\n星への祈り方も",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "なんだか、実家に加えて第３の我が家が\nできたみたいだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（それから……\n　私はしばらくルイネ州に留まることにした）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（両親の様子を見に実家に顔を出したり、\n　教会近くの魔物をカロリンと退治したり）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（今まで逃げてきたものを\n　清算するかのように過ごした）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ちゃんと向き合ってみれば。\n　向き合った分だけ、ちゃんと見つめ返してくれた）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（両親も。マザーシスターも）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私は、幸せ者だ）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "もう、よろしいのですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ああ。父さんと母さんの仲もだいぶ改善したし、\nもう大丈夫だよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "それは何よりですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "それじゃあ、行こうか。\nカロリンも来るんだったよね？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "はい。\n新たな旅路へ、共に参りましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]